<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About ESS</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
  <%- include('../components/topBanner') %>
  <%- include('../components/navbar') %>
<section class="relative flex flex-row items-center overflow-hidden h-[260px] sm:h-[320px] md:h-[430px]">
  <div class="w-1/2 text-white p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center"
       style="background: #000026; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 70% 100%, 0% 100%);">
    <h1 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
      Martin Shozi
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-1 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-xl font-medium text-gray-200">
      Chief Executive Officer (CEO)
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="w-1/2 h-full">
    <img 
      src="/images/user2.jpg" 
      alt="Martin Shozi" 
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>
</section>
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 p-6 bg-white font-sans">
    <div class="border-[6px] border-gray-200 rounded-sm shadow-md p-6 bg-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        A message from Martin
      </h2>
      <div class="relative w-full aspect-video rounded-sm shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <video id="essVideo"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0"
          poster="/images/martinVideo.jpg"
          controls>
          <source src="/videos/ess.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
        <div id="videoOverlay"
          onclick="playVideo()"
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-white cursor-pointer transition hover:bg-black/70 z-10">
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 drop-shadow-lg">MARTIN SHOZI</h3>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-6 drop-shadow-md">Founder · Ekhaya Smart Scholars</p>
          <i class="fas fa-play-circle text-6xl text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-6">
      Mr Martin Shozi is the visionary founder of Ekhaya Smart Scholars, an organization dedicated to improving access 
      to quality education for disadvantaged learners in rural and township communities. 
    </p>
    <div id="moreText" class="hidden mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <img src="/images/martin.JPG" alt="Martin Shozi" class="w-56 h-full shadow-md rounded-md object-contain" />
        <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center sm:text-left">
          Leadership Through Experience
        </h4>
      </div>
      <p>He pursued a Bachelor of Architecture (BA) degree under the Faculty of Engineering at the Durban University of Technology (DUT)...</p>
      <p>Growing up, Mr Martin experienced first-hand the challenges faced by learners who had the potential to succeed but were held back by a lack of academic support and resources.</p>
      <p>His journey has been marked by resilience and empathy — using his experiences as a catalyst for change rather than obstacles.</p>
      <p>It was from this realization that Ekhaya Smart Scholars was born, based on the belief that every learner deserves a second chance.</p>
      <p>The mission is to provide both online and physical tutoring tailored to underserved communities. Flexibility is one of its greatest strengths.</p>
    </div>
          <button id="toggleBtn"
        onclick="toggleMore()"
        class="mt-6 px-6 py-2 bg-blue-900 text-white font-semibold rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        View More
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="border-[6px] border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-sm shadow-md bg-green-100">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-3">Contact Martin</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-center text-gray-800 mb-4">
          Click below to share your feedback directly with Martin Shozi via WhatsApp.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <a href="https://wa.me/27614641899" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <button class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-900 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-md font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
              <i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Contact Me
            </button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-[6px] border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-sm shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Martin’s Post</h3>
        <img src="/images/picture.JPG" alt="ESS Event" class="w-full rounded-md shadow-md mb-3" />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
          Community upliftment event hosted by ESS in partnership with educators. The journey to impact starts here.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <script>
    function playVideo() {
      const video = document.getElementById("essVideo");
      const overlay = document.getElementById("videoOverlay");
      overlay.classList.add("hidden");
      video.play();
    }

    function toggleMore() {
      const moreText = document.getElementById('moreText');
      const btn = document.getElementById('toggleBtn');
      if (moreText.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        moreText.classList.remove('hidden');
        btn.textContent = 'View Less';
      } else {
        moreText.classList.add('hidden');
        btn.textContent = 'View More';
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>